00:35:35,416 --> 00:35:37,626
From the beginning. Get ready.

522
00:35:58,854 --> 00:36:01,189
Hey, skivvy. Don't forget my bed.

523
00:36:35,512 --> 00:36:37,014
February 15th.

524
00:36:37,097 --> 00:36:39,766
